						<summary>

						<p>Fragmentary slab lying in the field about a furlong to the north of the village.</p>						

						<p>1666 A.D.</p>						

						<p>The record is dated in the cyclic year Viśvāvasu, Māgha, śu. 13, Wednesday, and can be assigned to 17th century on the basis of palaeography. Hence the date of the record may be corresponded to 1666 A.D. Feruary, 7.</p>						

						<p>Registers the lease of land in the village Mīrāpuram. Saṁbaṭūru, Pāsīkalupādu given by Havaldar Hussain Sāheb.</p>						

						</summary>
